---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="博物北京品牌营销策划案">
  <main class="detail-page min-h-screen pt-24 pb-16">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">

      <!-- 返回按钮 -->
      <a href="/#portfolio" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-text-secondary hover:text-primary transition-colors mb-8">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <path d="M19 12H5M12 19l-7-7 7-7"/>
        </svg>
        返回首页
      </a>

      <!-- 头部信息 -->
      <div class="mb-12 animate-on-scroll">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4 gradient-text">博物北京品牌营销策划案</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-primary font-medium mb-4">打造北京"博物馆之城"文旅名片</p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-6">
          <span class="tag">品牌策划</span>
          <span class="tag">文旅营销</span>
          <span class="tag">产品设计</span>
          <span class="tag">媒体运营</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed max-w-3xl">
          围绕打造北京"博物馆之城"文旅名片，提出"博物北京"品牌，以企业化独立运营为模式，以"博物生活"为核心概念，构建「APP+衍生品+自有媒体」的产品体系，通过分阶段媒体运营和全年特色落地活动，将博物文化融入北京日常，实现文博产业专业化、产业化发展。
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Banner 图 -->
      <div class="mb-12 animate-on-scroll delay-100">
        <img
          src="/images/bowu-beijing-cover.jpg"
          alt="博物北京策划案"
          class="w-full rounded-2xl shadow-2xl"
        />
      </div>

      <!-- 品牌核心设定 -->
      <section class="mb-12 animate-on-scroll delay-200">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="w-1 h-6 bg-gradient-to-b from-primary to-secondary rounded-full"></span>
          品牌核心设定
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="rounded-xl bg-surface border border-border p-6">
            <h3 class="font-bold mb-3 text-primary flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-xl">🏛️</span>
              品牌名称与运营模式
            </h3>
            <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed">
              品牌名"博物北京"，兼顾北京城市属性与文博核心，<strong class="text-text">与政府保持相对独立的企业化运作</strong>，把控全市博物IP授权与媒体营销，提升操作灵活性；标识采用低饱和、扁平化现代风格+古典元素，大气简洁。
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-xl bg-surface border border-border p-6">
            <h3 class="font-bold mb-3 text-primary flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-xl">✨</span>
              核心概念
            </h3>
            <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed">
              <strong class="text-text text-lg">"活在一城，博物万象"（博物生活）</strong><br/>
              让文博古物"活"起来，将博物文化打造成北京特色城市生活方式，鼓励民众走入博物馆。
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-xl bg-surface border border-border p-6">
            <h3 class="font-bold mb-3 text-primary flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-xl">🎯</span>
              目标人群
            </h3>
            <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed">
              全民覆盖，细分5类核心人群——城市游览者、休闲乐活者、知识探索者、兴趣驱动者、云端在场者。
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- 三大核心产品 -->
      <section class="mb-12 animate-on-scroll delay-300">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="w-1 h-6 bg-gradient-to-b from-primary to-secondary rounded-full"></span>
          三大核心产品策略
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="rounded-xl bg-surface border border-border p-6">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-primary/20 text-primary flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg">1</div>
              <div class="flex-1">
                <h3 class="font-bold mb-2 text-lg">文博聚合 APP</h3>
                <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm mb-3">
                  定位博物馆"一卡通"、博物生活载体，核心功能包括<strong class="text-text">贴贴博物（NFC交互式讲解）</strong>、知识付费（听物板块）、与北京博物馆通票联动的年费制度；UI简洁无冗余，通过准捆绑售卖培养用户消费习惯。
                </p>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                  <span class="text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded bg-bg text-text-secondary">NFC 交互</span>
                  <span class="text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded bg-bg text-text-secondary">知识付费</span>
                  <span class="text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded bg-bg text-text-secondary">年费会员</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-xl bg-surface border border-border p-6">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-primary/20 text-primary flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg">2</div>
              <div class="flex-1">
                <h3 class="font-bold mb-2 text-lg">文博衍生品（分层运营）</h3>
                <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm mb-3">
                  <strong class="text-text">拾物</strong>：平价文创生活杂货子品牌，布局商场门店，主打日常化、生活化；<br/>
                  <strong class="text-text">新文玩</strong>：面向趣缘群体的高端收藏类产品，与分众博物馆联合开发、双重贴标，仅博物馆独家售卖，凸显稀缺性。
                </p>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                  <span class="text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded bg-bg text-text-secondary">平价文创</span>
                  <span class="text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded bg-bg text-text-secondary">高端收藏</span>
                  <span class="text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded bg-bg text-text-secondary">分层运营</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-xl bg-surface border border-border p-6">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-primary/20 text-primary flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg">3</div>
              <div class="flex-1">
                <h3 class="font-bold mb-2 text-lg">文博自有媒体</h3>
                <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm mb-3">
                  定位专业化文博资讯+故事媒体，打造融媒体矩阵，内容以<strong class="text-text">趣味资讯+普通人博物生活人物故事</strong>为主，区别于官方政务账号，同时联动品牌其他产品实现流量转化。
                </p>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                  <span class="text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded bg-bg text-text-secondary">融媒体矩阵</span>
                  <span class="text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded bg-bg text-text-secondary">人物故事</span>
                  <span class="text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded bg-bg text-text-secondary">流量转化</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- 核心亮点 -->
      <section class="mb-12 animate-on-scroll delay-400">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="w-1 h-6 bg-gradient-to-b from-primary to-secondary rounded-full"></span>
          策划案核心亮点
        </h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="rounded-xl bg-surface border border-border p-6">
            <h3 class="font-bold mb-3 text-primary flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-xl">🚀</span>
              运营模式创新
            </h3>
            <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm">
              政企分离的企业化运作，摒弃传统文博项目的强政府属性，既保留官方资源加持，又提升操作灵活性，避免年轻受众的对抗式解读。
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-xl bg-surface border border-border p-6">
            <h3 class="font-bold mb-3 text-primary flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-xl">💡</span>
              产品体系创新
            </h3>
            <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm">
              "贴贴博物"NFC交互式讲解是核心创新点，将讲解从"按键/扫码"升级为趣味互动，打破博物馆物理边界，延伸至公园、植物园等场景。
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-xl bg-surface border border-border p-6">
            <h3 class="font-bold mb-3 text-primary flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-xl">🎯</span>
              营销玩法创新
            </h3>
            <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm">
              全年热点话题运营+多元跨界联动，联名线条小狗、《乘风破浪的姐姐》、郭培等设计师，结合元宇宙、AI等新技术，打破文博"高冷感"。
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-xl bg-surface border border-border p-6">
            <h3 class="font-bold mb-3 text-primary flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-xl">🌍</span>
              场景延伸创新
            </h3>
            <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm">
              打破博物馆物理边界，将博物场景延伸至公园、地铁、商场、寺庙、高校等多元空间，实现"全域动态博物馆"。
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-xl bg-surface border border-border p-6">
            <h3 class="font-bold mb-3 text-primary flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-xl">📖</span>
              文化传播创新
            </h3>
            <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm">
              以"普通人的博物生活故事"为核心，用故事打动受众，将专业文博知识转化为大众易懂、感兴趣的内容，培养新的文博趣缘群体。
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-xl bg-surface border border-border p-6">
            <h3 class="font-bold mb-3 text-primary flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-xl">👥</span>
              用户运营创新
            </h3>
            <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm">
              通过集章、电子勋章、虚拟钱币、博物存钱罐、盲盒路线等趣味激励机制，提升用户参与度与粘性，培养博物消费习惯。
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- 媒体运营策略 -->
      <section class="mb-12 animate-on-scroll delay-500">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="w-1 h-6 bg-gradient-to-b from-primary to-secondary rounded-full"></span>
          分阶段媒体运营策略
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="rounded-xl bg-surface border border-border p-6">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
              <span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-primary/20 text-primary text-sm font-bold">1-2月</span>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-lg">蓄势期</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm">网络倡导博物生活理念，完成产品研发</p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-xl bg-surface border border-border p-6">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
              <span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-primary/20 text-primary text-sm font-bold">3-4月</span>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-lg">登场期</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm">上线全产品，吸引本地人群体验，形成口碑</p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-xl bg-surface border border-border p-6">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
              <span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-primary/20 text-primary text-sm font-bold">5-10月</span>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-lg">作为期</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm">旅游旺季发力，提升品牌知名度与忠诚度</p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-xl bg-surface border border-border p-6">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
              <span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-primary/20 text-primary text-sm font-bold">11-12月</span>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-lg">衔接期</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm">评估效果，衔接2025年计划</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- 平台策略 -->
      <section class="mb-12 animate-on-scroll delay-600">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="w-1 h-6 bg-gradient-to-b from-primary to-secondary rounded-full"></span>
          全平台精准布局
        </h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
          <div class="rounded-xl bg-surface border border-border p-5 text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl mb-2">📱</div>
            <h3 class="font-bold mb-2">微博</h3>
            <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm">话题营销主阵地<br/>引导公共议程</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl bg-surface border border-border p-5 text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl mb-2">📺</div>
            <h3 class="font-bold mb-2">B站</h3>
            <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm">挖掘兴趣内容<br/>吸引亚文化圈层</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl bg-surface border border-border p-5 text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl mb-2">📔</div>
            <h3 class="font-bold mb-2">小红书</h3>
            <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm">打造文旅攻略<br/>占领内容优势</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl bg-surface border border-border p-5 text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl mb-2">🎵</div>
            <h3 class="font-bold mb-2">抖音</h3>
            <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm">覆盖全年龄<br/>重点触达儿童家长</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl bg-surface border border-border p-5 text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl mb-2">💭</div>
            <h3 class="font-bold mb-2">知乎</h3>
            <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm">理性长文<br/>说服城市高知群体</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<script>
  const observer = new IntersectionObserver(
    (entries) => {
      entries.forEach((entry) => {
        if (entry.isIntersecting) {
          entry.target.classList.add("visible");
        }
      });
    },
    { threshold: 0.1 }
  );
  document.querySelectorAll(".animate-on-scroll").forEach((el) => {
    observer.observe(el);
  });
</script>
